The universe hums with it, a constant, unseen thrum. Energy. You want to understand it? Fine. But don't expect hand-holding. I'll give you the facts, the cold, hard, unassailable truths, just as they are laid out. And perhaps, if you're exceptionally dull, I'll even elaborate. Just try not to waste my time.

